{"tid":118584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我老母話M記個雪糕好多人排隊","createTime":"2017-02-13T06:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T10:39:37.000Z","uid":57357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56c1e8c7fb9dec65c34b10f2df67fb3191c2974d","tid":118584,"uid":57357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:27:24.000Z","msg":"話說尋日行街經過M記，見到雪糕counter個到排到勁長龍，一向唔多食M記既我就講左句: 嘩! 乜咁多人排隊，有咩新野食?<br />\n<br />\n之後我阿媽就話: 出左新雪糕吖嗎，mario雪糕呀，好多人食架你要唔要試下?<br />\n<br />\n我心諗: M記整mario雪糕仲要咁多人排隊，莫非真係少有佳作? 正常出呢D噱頭野，圖片同實物一定係好撚不符，咁多人排隊一定唔會伏得去邊。好，咁我就試下佢，由於太多人排既關係我就排左五分鐘到，終於到我個陣心知不妙，點解個個人手上既雪糕都唔係mario，唔通又係D濕鳩大抽獎，頭獎有得玩mario?<br />\n<br />\n結果我抬頭一睇，仆你個街原來係oreo雪糕....."},{"pid":"54ad64f81b2d0c0f68128002852914238c4bb6a0","tid":118584,"uid":54736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e62c27cfbb0bd806b248241913345c761ad9f4","tid":118584,"uid":42299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36419157653cc1f1ca1e701e9b0065d49f12af74","tid":118584,"uid":21319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:32:39.000Z","msg":"😂"},{"pid":"4237e5acebffec0ee10d45a7b676b6ddca9f27a6","tid":118584,"uid":22599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:33:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b679cf63d391b7abc4fb01931b236a759fee095","tid":118584,"uid":7923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:33:51.000Z","msg":"重作"},{"pid":"991bef60872a42123abf621b9c731a1f6e4100e4","tid":118584,"uid":14486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/don